Logical Model: Child Report Logical Model

Official URL: https://www.ehealth.fgov.be/standards/fhir/childrecord/StructureDefinition/BeModelChildReport Version: 0.1.0
Computable Name: BeModelChildReport

A logical model representing child report data elements.

Usages:

  • This Logical Model is not used by any profiles in this Implementation Guide

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
